Benchmark ESPP++ vs LAMMPS
==========================

Compiling
---------
* Use the following options for configure:
  --disable-logging
  CXXFLAGS=-O3

Running
-------

Generation of input file data.lj:

  gen.py   -> generates data.lj with 8.000 particles on a lattice

Note: data.lj is used as input file for both LAMMPS and ESPP++

NVE
===

Running 1000 iterations with cutoff 2.5

Timestep: 0.005

a) Running lammps

   lmpp < nve.lmp

b) Running ESPResSo++

   nve.py

